lead_paragraph: Teddy Bridgewater was sharp in his return from a sore arm, completing 12 of 16 passes for 161 yards and a touchdown in the first half for the Minnesota Vikings in a 23-10 exhibition victory Sunday over the San Diego Chargers in the official unveiling their new stadium.

headline.print_headline: Bridgewater, Vikings Beat Chargers 23-10 in Stadium Opener
